        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>silver halide [300130942], silver compounds [300127427], silver, silver compounds, alloys [300241467], nonferrous metal [300011014], metal by composition or origin [300010901], metal [300010900], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
